Job Description-***
-Manages the recruitment process to ensure qualified applicants are selected
-Conducts interviews with short listed candidates and makes recommendations and offers
-Develops and maintains relationship with employment agencies, universities and other recruitment sources
-Fosters effective communication between employees and management
-Analyses the effectiveness of recruitment result
-Other ad hoc tasks as requested by the supervisors.

Requirements:
-Bachelor degree or above, with major in human resources or business administration;
-At least 5+ years HR working experience, with the experience in headhunting will be an advantage;
-Strong sense of responsibility, maturity and teamwork;
-Able to work independently and under pressure;
-Impressive interpersonal skills and problem solving skills;
-Good communication and coordination, good sense of team work.
